{{cite news| url=http://southtownstar.suntimes.com/southtown/columns/vickroy/x07-dvy2.htm | archive-url=https://archive.today/20110721221948/http://southtownstar.suntimes.com/southtown/columns/vickroy/x07-dvy2.htm | url-status=dead | archive-date=July 21, 2011 | work=Chicago Sun-Times}}
